eddy.lang

Class Type

  • java.lang.Object
    • eddy.lang.Type

  • public class Type
extends java.lang.Object
    Describes a conceptual relationship between two or more RoleValues. This includes whether the concepts are Actor, Datum, or Purpose, and whether the left-hand concept subsumes, is subsumed by, is disjoint from, or is equivalent to the concepts on the right-hand side.
    Author:
    Travis Breaux
